text: Marsel Markulin (29 October 1936 - 1 April 2009) was a Croatian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2009 deaths Category:Croatian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb
